How do incubators work?


Incubate - Startup team or company that is pre-product on market
Accelerate - Increase released product of company

Incubators/Investors
	Need tangibles to get investments (especially games)
	Build up a game (or even portfolio) before approaching funding level
			Team, ready to go, personal - team level funding for mean time
	They sometimes are middle men for other investors who have no idea of industries..


